---
title: Balsamic Mushroom-and-Brie Flatbreads with Lemony Pine Nut Gremolata
description: Sautéed onions and mushrooms are the base for perfectly melted brie on this flatbread. Toasted pine nuts spiked with lemon and parsley deliver satisfying crunch. This meal is simple to prepare but special enough for a weeknight celebration!

